Bundle ID: com.devtools.moonlander
==================================


Leaderboards        Name                                ID
============        ==========================          =======================================
                    moonlander.mcdonalds                com.devtools.moonlander.mcdonalds.leaderboard
                    


McDonalds Scoring
=================
Score is 

500 - abs(distance)
    - time
    + fuel
    - 10 * abs(angle)
    - 10 * abs(vervel)
    - 10 * abs(horvel)


